title: O’Malley won’t share his fundraising total, but he has written a song about it
text: Unlike his leading rivals, Democratic presidential hopeful Martin O’Malley has yet to disclose how much money he raised during the past quarter. But the former governor of Maryland did put out a song about it on Monday. In a video uploaded to YouTube, O’Malley, who has a side career as a Celtic rock musician, is […] ...
